                          DChat - Peer-To-Peer Chat over TOR 

  FORMAT
  ------

    The following astyle format options are used for the source files of this project:

    astyle --style=allman --indent=spaces=4 --indent-switches --indent-preproc-define \
    --indent-col1-comments --min-conditional-indent=0 --break-blocks --pad-header     \
    --delete-empty-lines --align-pointer=type --add-brackets --convert-tabs           \
    --max-code-length=80 --break-after-logical --mode=c
